{"tid":1392524,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"謝謝香港人送前線物資 但你中計啦！","createTime":"2019-07-31T18:45:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T16:38:42.000Z","uid":90560,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bf9a9661ed9da9fbfda34f47010c8f4d7546175c","tid":1392524,"uid":90560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:45:53.000Z","msg":"利申 標題黨<br />\n<br />\n香港人係好有愛，一呼百應，但好容易會有「爆發」的情況出現，就好似捐血咁，每當有大型事故就會有好多人排住隊一窩蜂咁捐，最後有部分血就會因為過期而浪費.<br />\n<br />\n而物資都好容易會出現呢個問題，尤其好多人都唔敢囤積太多物資係身，因為會驚俾警犬周. 萬一星期六/日物資站物資過剩，到時前線為咗唔浪費就要冒險將物資分散 keep. 風險大咗之餘又要擔心俾警犬掃物資，到時大家的心意就白費咗.<br />\n<br />\n所以我建議<br />\n-大家盡量唔好將物資囤積係物資站，以免搬竇/逃跑唔方便，避免警犬一次過沒收哂啲物資<br />\n-視乎情況分批排發物資，例如買咗20個豬嘴就今日派10個，聽日派10個. 有時前線為咗逃跑真係會焗住棄物資... 抗爭的路可能仲有好長，萬一下星期就又無哂物資都唔知點算，始終後排keep物資的風險比前線低好多<br />\n<br />\n前線最需要的係人，如果可以就親身落場支持，或者參與罷工、多啲關心下街上做文宣的示威者. <br />\n<br />\n再一次多謝香港人的愛，小小愚見，都係想物資同大家的心意可以用得其所，歡迎討論<br />\n<br />\n另外 8 月 5 日我會罷工！光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"0a87accdd94fd53349a6b64116972db5045fd110","tid":1392524,"uid":262091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T22:55:57.000Z","msg":"召喚冷氣戰士入黎一人一信<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">反對黑警加人工! </span></strong></span>黑警你憑咩?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1388116\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1388116</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n記得要加減wordings!!!幫手推"},{"pid":"46da350990391da372fba4ca7e2911dfab42dad6","tid":1392524,"uid":187489,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:35:23.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n太集中好危險<br />\n<br />\n原意係好好 只係太多賤人有心人 最緊要知道啲狗係好冇品"},{"pid":"d9c92b3ce19b46b72d3aa99b3be9dd48d2df5e4c","tid":1392524,"uid":90560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:34:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B0oMXIBlbKQ/?igshid=1qss7so0mo6tf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB0oMXIBlbKQ%2F%3Figshid%3D1qss7so0mo6tf&d=puaUx2dgpXXsrsLU9noyGAsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=e192be9c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB0oMXIBlbKQ%2F%3Figshid%3D1qss7so0mo6tf&h=645d7b9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B0oMXIBlbKQ/?igshid=1qss7so0mo6tf</a><br />\n哎屌 真係收哂啲物資 仆街死黑警"},{"pid":"c87288516eee0ebe8cedd2592ddcbc2acf09cf19","tid":1392524,"uid":102214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:36:16.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"13b633fea4e0c2e83cfc243b92a8310b5246c013","tid":1392524,"uid":90560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:38:42.000Z","msg":"警搜火炭物資倉拉2人 防暴警出動大批市民到場聲援<br />\n<br />\n晚上10時許，大批警方在火炭喜利佳工業大廈進行調查，其間在一單位內發現一批物資及急救用品，並拘捕至少兩名男子。大批市民收到消息後趕往現場了解，要求警方交代事件，其後數十名防暴警到場增援，又要求在場的市民離開，並關上大廈閘門，阻止市民入內，雙方正在對峙中，氣氛緊張，<br />\n<br />\n據知，被捕2人事後送往沙田警署，過百名市民得悉事件後，趕往警署聲援，要求警方放人，又高呼：「香港警察，知法犯法」，其間警署的報案室拉上鐵閘，市民用雜物堵塞警署出入口。立法會議員林卓廷其後亦有到場，要求與指揮官對話。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190801/59887752/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190801%2F59887752%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=puaUx2dgpXXsrsLU9noyGAsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=72f4b224\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190801%2F59887752%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=b6892e60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190801/59887752/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"}]}